         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 1034, recto: (1) I, Isaac, son of Paul, (2) the husbandman of (3) the scholasticus, write (4) to Plebe, the man of Jeme, (5) saying: I owe you five (6) artabas of wheat, and these (7) I am prepared to (8) give to you in Paone (9) of the second (year) without any (10) dispute (11) ...I have written this...</ab>
